# Markers of control vs low_salt up/down regulation

type_markers <- FindMarkers(
  object = SO4,
  ident.1 = "low_salt",   
  ident.2 = "control",     
  group.by = "treatment",
  min.pct = 0.1,           
  logfc.threshold = 0.25,  
  only.pos = FALSE         
)
